  • :
    1. Support: itemset data support(x) = count(x) / N
    2. Confidence: rule (x -> y) x confidence(x -> y) = support(x,y) / support(x)
    3. Lift: rule items Lift 1 lift(x -> y) = support(x,y) / support(x) * support(y)

apriori rules lift > 1 87 rulesitemset = 2 66 itemset 3 21 10 rules 

rules <- apriori(Groceries, parameter = list(supp = 0.014222222, conf = 0.25, minlen=2))
rules <- sort(rules, decreasing = T, by = "confidence")
# filter lift < 1  rules
rules <- subset(rules, lift > 1)
